{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kijutsu Rider is a fast paced third person hack and slash anime styled action game where you play as one of five unstoppable heroes, carve your way through waves of monstrous enemies, take down the black cross conglomerate and save the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/COMBAT.png?t=1738119175\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use a mix of Parries, Dodges, Counters, and Guard Breaks, along with an arsenal of special moves and combos to obliterate the hordes of enemies coming your way in an explosive high speed action combat system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/rr_combo.gif?t=1738119175\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/CHARACTERS.png?t=1738119175\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Rei &quot;RED RIDER&quot; Ryder</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/RR_SplashArt1.png?t=1738119175\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rookie Cop turned vigilante Motorcycle Wizard, Rei makes use of his multi form Nitro calibur blade to unleash high speed high damage attacks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/rr_light.gif?t=1738119175\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/rr_HEAVY.gif?t=1738119175\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ANN SU RA</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/ann_splash1.png?t=1738119175\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Heiress to the Pharaoh Triad crime family turned beast street Yakuza enforcer, Ann makes use of wide reaching whip attack and explosive earth constructs to dominate the battlefield</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/ann_combo.gif?t=1738119175\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>KIBA YAMAKIBA</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/kibaSplash.png?t=1738119175\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A wild yakuza runner who uses his beastial instinct to dance across the battle field carving through his foes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/kiba_combo.gif?t=1738119175\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">*<strong>MORE COMING SOON</strong>*<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/BOSS_BATTLES.png?t=1738119175\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/extras/bossLineUpHS.png?t=1738119175\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kijutsu Rider features 15 unique levels, over 25 unique enemy types, and 10 intense boss fights, to push the players skill and reflexes to their absolute limits\u00a0\u00a0</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3474960?t=1738119175","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3474960?t=1738119175","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474960/568f6441c9229c0e843c9e32a74096e1f1c2ba60/cap